# FlipFezo Project Rules

## Deployment

- When user types "deploy" in terminal, run: `D:\GitHub\FlipIQ\FlipFezo\deploy.ps1`
- The deploy script uses this default commit message: "Update FlipFezo: Money Partner Application - web assets, navigation, and features"
- User can override with custom message: `deploy "Custom message here"`

## Project Structure

- Main web assets: `apps/web/assets/`
- Splash screen: `apps/web/assets/splash/`
- React components: `apps/web/src/components/` (if using React)

## Navigation Order

1. Home (index.html)
2. Application (application.html)
3. Project Team (introduction.html) - was "Introduction"
4. Feasibility (feasibility.html)
5. Comparable Sold (comparable-sold.html)
6. Contract of Sale (contract-of-sale.html)

## Setup (Admin-Only)

- Setup gear (⚙️) is hidden by default
- Visible only with `?setup=1` in URL
- Admin-only configuration for email, notifications, environment
